Who I Am

About Me

"Design that drives results — not just looks."

I'm Carmela (Mela) Febra — a B2B Multimedia Designer from the Philippines specializing in design that converts. I create high-impact brochures, presentations, and eBooks that support sales, lead generation, and executive decision-making.

Alongside print, I craft visually engaging brand assets including social media banners, campaign materials, animations, and website content — all built to align creative direction with real business objectives.
